HANNSTAR DISPLAY said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 24.43% to NT$2,945,101,000 from NT$3,897,258,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           2,945,101        3,897,258   
YOY%             -24.43%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           11,205,441       14,429,653  
YOY%             -22.34% 
=================================================================
 